data.text:
About Santa Cruz Tenerife

Santa Cruz Tenerife is located at the eastern tip of the Spanish island of Tenerife. The city has extremely exciting nightlife and gorgeous beaches, which are perfect for sunbathing, swimming and water-sports. The city also has a lively cultural scene, museums and art galleries to enjoy. There are also superb restaurants serving local cuisine and fresh seafood dishes. Every February the city hosts the spectacular Santa Cruz carnival. The city is also well known for its excellent shopping.

Football matches in Santa Cruz Tenerife

You can enjoy some excellent and exciting football at the city's stadium. Santa Cruz Tenerife football tickets can be purchased at livefootballtickets.com. So if you are visiting the city, why not check out some great football?
